{{Quote|It was as if they were, force-dead...|[[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] to [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]]|<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide I: Onslaught">''[[The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide I: Onslaught]]''</ref>}}
'''"Force-dead"''' was a term used by a handful of [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] to describe the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]'s absence of being [[Force sense/Legends|sensed]] through [[The Force/Legends|the Force]]. [[Lumiya]] also had the ability to [[Force stealth|cloak]] herself from being sensed in the Force.

After using his unique form of [[Force healing/Legends|Force healing]], [[Cade Skywalker]] was cut off from the Force.

